tip.text: Egg toast & mac and cheese are to die for. Oh and of course the legendary buttermilk fried chicken. FAWESOME.

Good bold flavours w decent ambiance. Definitely a winner.
Lovely space with great coffees by second best barista of 2014!
One of a kind venue with eye popping art and fine French food. Every art fiend's wet dream. Alex, Tim and Monique behind the bar make fantastic cocktails too.
Massage was sensational. But def loved the entire holistic COMO package more.
